    "abstract": "We give an interpretation of the Maxi\u00ad mum Entropy (MaxEnt) Principle in game\u00ad theoretic terms. Based on this interpretation, we make a formal distinction between differ\u00ad ent ways of applying Maximum Entropy dis\u00ad tributions. MaxEnt has frequently been crit\u00ad icized on the grounds that it leads to highly representation dependent results. Our dis\u00ad tinction allows us to avoid this problem in many cases.",
